give @p written_book{pages:['["",{"text":"The Night of the Living Dead","italic":true},{"text":" is a horror movie that released in 1968, and is considered one of the first modern day zombie films. \\nThe movie was regarded as a huge touchstone for horror movies, releasing before the main movie rating system did.","color":"reset"}]','{"text":"The movie had explicit violence and gore, which got both positive and negative reviews.\\n\\nThe plot of the movie is that a brother and sister are going to visit their fathers grave, in rural Pennsylvania. As they leave the grave, a man attacks them, killing"}','{"text":"the brother. The sister flees to an abandoned farmhouse, where she meets more survivors and one of them drives off the ghouls approaching them. \\n\\nThey find out on the radio that all across the East Coast of the U.S., there has been large"}','{"text":"groups of cannibalistic, coming back to life corpses, and that groups of armed men are going across the countryside to kill the ghouls.\\n\\nOne of the survivors though was bitten by a ghoul, and a couple of them decide to try to"}','{"text":"get medical supplies and fuel for a truck.\\n\\nThey go to a gas station, but ultimately it results in killing two out of the three people after the truck catches fire and explodes.\\n\\nThe survivor heads back to the farmhouse,"}','{"text":"where a fight between the other survivors breaks out, and ghouls break through the barricades. \\n\\nThe bitten survivor also turns into a ghoul, and soon all the survivors except one have been turned or killed."}','{"text":"The lone survivor hides in the cellar, before eventually being woken up in the morning by a group of armed men, but they mistake him for a ghoul, ultimately killing him, and burning his body with the rest of the killed ghouls."}'],title:"Night of the Living Dead Article",author:Gurkk80} 1
